          <p>以下是 Webhooks 通知地址配置的 <code>charge.succeeded</code> 对象的示例：</p>
          <div class="code-filter alipay_qr"><div class="channel-description">alipay_qr</div>
          <pre><code class="language-json"><div class="code"><pre class="hljs"><div class="line">{</div><div class="line">    <span class="hljs-attr">"id"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"evt_4Y1aP31wJYE07CpxIaIrNJWy"</span>,</div><div class="line">    <span class="hljs-attr">"created"</span>: <span class="hljs-number">1458736932</span>,</div><div class="line">    <span class="hljs-attr">"livemode"</span>: <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>,</div><div class="line">    <span class="hljs-attr">"type"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"charge.succeeded"</span>,</div><div class="line">    <span class="hljs-attr">"data"</span>: {</div><div class="line">        <span class="hljs-attr">"object"</span>: {</div><div class="line">            <span class="hljs-attr">"id"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"ch_Tiv5K0y98GCK0eP8e9j1O8S4"</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="hljs-attr">"object"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"charge"</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="hljs-attr">"created"</span>: <span class="hljs-number">1458736905</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="hljs-attr">"livemode"</span>: <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="hljs-attr">"paid"</span>: <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="hljs-attr">"refunded"</span>: <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="hljs-attr">"app"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"app_1Gqj58ynP0mHeX1q"</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="hljs-attr">"channel"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"alipay_qr"</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="hljs-attr">"order_no"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"123456789"</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="hljs-attr">"client_ip"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"116.228.208.114"</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="hlj